## 🧩 组件规范

### 按钮组件

#### 主要按钮 (Primary Button)
```css
.btn-primary {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color) 0%, var(--primary-light) 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 10px 24px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    border: none;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px 0 rgba(0, 110, 255, 0.2);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.btn-primary:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px 0 rgba(0, 110, 255, 0.3);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
}
```

#### 次要按钮 (Secondary Button)
```css
.btn-secondary {
    background: white;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    border: 1px solid var(--primary-color);
    padding: 10px 24px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.btn-secondary:hover {
    background: var(--primary-lighter);
}
```

#### 文字按钮 (Text Button)
```css
.btn-text {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    border: none;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    font-size: 14px;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.btn-text:hover {
    background: var(--primary-lighter);
}
```

#### 按钮尺寸规范
- **大按钮**: `padding: 12px 32px; font-size: 16px; height: 48px;`
- **标准按钮**: `padding: 10px 24px; font-size: 14px; height: 40px;`
- **小按钮**: `padding: 6px 16px; font-size: 13px; height: 32px;`

### 信息卡片

#### IP资产卡片
```css
.ip-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 0;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-primary);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    overflow: hidden;
}

.ip-card:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
}
```

#### 数据卡片
```css
.data-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 20px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-primary);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
}

.data-card-title {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.data-card-value {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
}
```

### 表单组件

#### 输入框
```css
.form-input {
    width: 100%;
    height: 40px;
    padding: 0 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-primary);
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    background: white;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.form-input:hover {
    border-color: var(--primary-light);
}

.form-input:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--primary-color);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(0, 110, 255, 0.1);
}

.form-input::placeholder {
    color: var(--text-placeholder);
}
```

#### 选择框
```css
.form-select {
    width: 100%;
    height: 40px;
    padding: 0 32px 0 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-primary);
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-size: 14px;
    background: white;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
}
```

#### 标签
```css
.form-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.form-label-required::after {
    content: '*';
    color: var(--error-color);
    margin-left: 4px;
}
```

### 弹窗组件
```css
.modal-mask {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: var(--bg-mask);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    z-index: 1000;
}

.modal-content {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
    max-width: 600px;
    width: 90%;
    max-height: 80vh;
    overflow: hidden;
}

.modal-header {
    padding: 20px 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-primary);
}

.modal-body {
    padding: 24px;
    max-height: calc(80vh - 140px);
    overflow-y: auto;
}

.modal-footer {
    padding: 16px 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-primary);
    text-align: right;
}
```

### 影视剧海报展示

#### 海报容器（3:4尺寸）
```css
.poster-container {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    padding-top: 133.33%; /* 3:4 = 4/3 = 133.33% */
    border-radius: 6px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f2f5 0%, #e5e7eb 100%);
}

.poster-image {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
}

.poster-placeholder {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e6f2ff 0%, #f0f6ff 100%);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 16px;
}
```

**使用示例**：
```html
<!-- 有海报图片 -->
<div class="poster-container">
    <img src="poster.jpg" alt="IP名称" class="poster-image">
</div>

<!-- 无海报占位 -->
<div class="poster-container">
    <div class="poster-placeholder">IP名称</div>
</div>
```

